_sText:
Play tested to death and beyond the third version of ba_ironman.
See the read me file for additional information an additions and fixes.

Ba_iron_man_final is a combine themed prison break map set out side. It includes a infirmary, watch tower, armory, party room, big cage, high spray contest wall, sauna, two traps, knife fight (kf)/ chicken fight (cf) area, war area, pool, cells for ts, plenty of secret rooms and shot for shot / deagle toss area.
